

INSTALL INSTRUCTIONS:
This Application is designed to live in it's own domain or sub domain. Currently it can be dropped into the public folder as is. 

For heightened security add js/ media/ css/ .htaccess and index.php to public directory. Keep all other directories out of the way of port 80. If you choose the more secure installation. Please edit lines: 29 & 47 in index.php to appropriate paths.

the SQL directory contains a single MySQL structure that will need to be installed

application/config/database.php will need to be configured to the MySQL credentials of your server.


This application was built using 

Codeigniter http://codeigniter.com/user_guide/database/index.html
jQuery http://jquery.com/

